(patch 1000 files at a time) Ensure all E&P ethnicity preset files contain a consistent set of eye / brow gene blocks so downstream tools can rely on their presence. 
Perform the update in batches to avoid huge single-run edits and stay within tool size limits.
Description
Insert the following gene blocks when absent into epe genes/ethnicities/e&p*.txt files: gene_eye_size, gene_eye_shut_top, gene_eye_shut_bottom, gene_forehead_inner_brow_width, and gene_bs_eye_fold_2. 
The insertion logic appends the missing blocks just before the final closing brace of each preset and preserves existing file BOM/EOF behavior by decoding/encoding with utf-8-sig.

Only files missing any of the target gene keys are to be modified; files that already contained all five blocks are to be left untouched.
